SELECT model_name, manufacturer, power_output FROM wind_turbine_models JOIN performance_data ON wind_turbine_models.model_id = performance_data.model_id WHERE power_output > 500 ORDER BY power_output DESC
SELECT * FROM maintenance_records WHERE maintenance_type LIKE 'routine%' AND technician_name = 'John Doe' ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC

SELECT model_name, maintenance_type, resolution FROM wind_turbine_models JOIN maintenance_records ON wind_turbine_models.model_id = maintenance_records.model_id JOIN fault_logs ON maintenance_records.record_id = fault_logs.record_id WHERE resolution IS NOT NULL ORDER BY model_name, maintenance_type ASC

SELECT timestamp, location, temperature, wind_speed FROM WeatherData WHERE temperature < 0 OR wind_speed > 20 ORDER BY location ASC, timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
